001package com.technototes.library.logger.entry;
002
003import com.technototes.library.util.Color;
004import java.util.function.Supplier;
005
006public class BooleanEntry extends Entry<Boolean> {
007
008    private String trueEntry, falseEntry;
009
010    public BooleanEntry(String n, Supplier<Boolean> s, int index, String wt, String wf) {
011        super(n, s, index);
012        trueEntry = wt;
013        falseEntry = wf;
014    }
015
016    @Override
017    public String toString() {
018        return (get() ? trueEntry : falseEntry);
019    }
020}
